<item>
            <title>[LU-2733] lustre-initialization-1: mgs_init0()) MGS: MGS filesystem method init failed: rc = -2</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2733</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/1ce6075a-6c05-11e2-b2a5-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/1ce6075a-6c05-11e2-b2a5-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre-initialization_1 failed with the following error in the MDS console log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mgs_init0()) MGS: MGS filesystem method init failed: rc = -2
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and the following in the client autotest log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Starting mds1: -o user_xattr,acl  lustre-mdt1/mdt1 /mnt/mds1
mkdir -p /mnt/mds1; mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,acl lustre-mdt1/mdt1 /mnt/mds1
mount.lustre: mount lustre-mdt1/mdt1 at /mnt/mds1 failed: No such file or directory
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: lustre-initialization-1 lustre-initialization_1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
